modName: Race Menu Preset - Audrienne Rolaine - DELETED
descriptionHtml:
Place this in the Data folder
Ingame open up the console and type showracemenu.
At the race menu select the breton race and set the preset slider to 0 and press F9.

Requirements:
SG Hairs 268 (Google it)
Improved Eyes Skyrim (Maybe)


The save game this character is based on is by Dennis05
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/188881/?
Make sure to visit his profile and give him a Kudos point.
author: LittleFighter
